quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ďe wi\"i: \"Menen, ko men halkoo…ďee yim…ďe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ďe mayre laatike too√Īoo…ďe"
  29,32,"O maaki: \"Kono Luutu no ton!\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko menen …ďuri anndude fii won…ďe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kanko e yim…ďe makko …ďen, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ďe …ďen"
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen hewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ď…ďe, …ďernde makko …ďi…ótorii fii ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, wata a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ďe ma an e …ďeynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ďe …ďen"
  29,34,"Ko men jippinoo…ďe lepte e yim…ďe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ďe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon"
  29,35,"Gom…óii Men accii e nden (saare), maande …ďanngunde, wonannde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe …ďen"
  29,36,"(Men nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, rewee Alla, jortoron √Ďalannde sakkitiinde nden, wata woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ďe"
  29,37,"Kono …ďe fenni mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ďe, …ďe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-maayi"
  29,38,"(Men halki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. Gom…óii caambbeje ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ďe, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, ndu sakkii …ďe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ďe rentunoo…ďe"
